            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "起動ボタンを OS のスクリーンショット・録画に写す"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Shows a launch button on screen so you can launch a report from it. (You can also launch by shaking the device twice.)" : {
      "comment" : "SettingsView: footer for the display section.",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "画面上に起動ボタンを表示し、そこからレポートを起動できます。（端末を2回振っても起動できます。）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
